| `delete`, `archive`, `complete` | -1 | MINUS | All |
| `update`, `label`, `share` | 0 | ERGODIC | All |
| `invite`, `schedule` | +1 | PLUS | Calendar, Meet |
| `export`, `formula` | 0 | ERGODIC | Docs, Sheets |
\stopverb}
}

